{"tid":167417,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"NASA 與霍金合作建造迷你飛船，以五分一光速飛行","createTime":"2017-03-22T20:40:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-23T14:45:45.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2313ffd68259b3b0af63284317ffb8b8daaa3a94","tid":167417,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T20:40:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://tomorrowsci.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/%E6%98%9F%E9%9A%9B%E6%99%B6%E7%89%87%E5%85%89%E9%80%9F-678x381.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftomorrowsci.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2F%25E6%2598%259F%25E9%259A%259B%25E6%2599%25B6%25E7%2589%2587%25E5%2585%2589%25E9%2580%259F-678x381.jpg&h=73196f10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國太空總處 NASA 正與史提芬霍金合作，研究建造一艘能以五分一光速飛行的迷你飛船。如研究成功，這艘名為「StarChip」（星際晶片）的飛船只需 20 年的時間，便可到達最鄰近地球的星系&mdash;&mdash;半人馬座 &alpha;。<br />\n<br />\n「星際晶片」顧名思義，是一塊 2.5 釐米大的晶片，連接著一面 3.6 米的「光帆」，以地球射出的激光為動力，加速至五分一光速。<br />\n<br />\n太空輻射<br />\n<br />\n這個計劃由霍金於四月份公布，由他與韓國科學技術院合作進行。但多月來，他們一直未能解決一個難題：如何讓飛船抵受 20 年的太空輻射。根據研究顯示，太空中的高能量輻射有可能導致飛船在完成任務之前，便完全停止運作。<br />\n<br />\n而 NASA 便正正可以在這方面提供援助。上週，NASA 於舊金山舉行的國際電子元件會議（IEDM）中，發表了他們的建議：<br />\n<br />\n第一，調整飛船的飛航路線，盡量避免高輻射地帶。但這方法將會加長飛航時間，並未必能完全解決問題。<br />\n<br />\n第二，NASA 建議飛船可以加上保護層，但這將會增加飛船的體積及重量，減慢飛航速度。<br />\n<br />\n第三，NASA 研究員建議使用一塊能自我修復的矽晶片。NASA 小組表示：「自我修復晶片技術已存在了很多年的時間。」他們相信，這技術將可令飛船在承受輻射傷害時自動修復，安全抵達目的地。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tomorrowsci.com/science/nasa-%E9%9C%8D%E9%87%91-%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C%E5%BB%BA%E9%80%A0-%E8%BF%B7%E4%BD%A0%E9%A3%9B%E8%88%B9-%E4%BA%94%E5%88%86%E4%B8%80%E5%85%89%E9%80%9F%E9%A3%9B%E8%A1%8C/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftomorrowsci.com%2Fscience%2Fnasa-%25E9%259C%258D%25E9%2587%2591-%25E5%2590%2588%25E4%25BD%259C%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E9%2580%25A0-%25E8%25BF%25B7%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E9%25A3%259B%25E8%2588%25B9-%25E4%25BA%2594%25E5%2588%2586%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2585%2589%25E9%2580%259F%25E9%25A3%259B%25E8%25A1%258C%2F&d=r5q0VKZH5TKX5M4XK8oFTRxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=f6ee9fc1\" target=\"_blank\">https://tomorrowsci.com/science/nasa-%E9%9C%8D%E9%87%91-%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C%E5%BB%BA%E9%80%A0-%E8%BF%B7%E4%BD%A0%E9%A3%9B%E8%88%B9-%E4%BA%94%E5%88%86%E4%B8%80%E5%85%89%E9%80%9F%E9%A3%9B%E8%A1%8C/</a>"},{"pid":"5de66e9bc19b21f261806cb7925cf645e74e79c9","tid":167417,"uid":36715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T21:24:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.metalbridges.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/GundamSEED-C.E.73-Stargazer-6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metalbridges.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F05%2FGundamSEED-C.E.73-Stargazer-6.jpg&h=bff1ebd8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9a0a7e94ebfde5fe90319ebbfe5492273a4090d8","tid":167417,"uid":60015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T22:10:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 渣ga<br />\n我跑仲快過佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61997d6f7519b6685a2fccd60983741cad6effa1","tid":167417,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T02:34:44.000Z","msg":"我射上天都唔止呢個速度噠"},{"pid":"e922e316a03d3294d2857f4df9c023fcdc6ff2dd","tid":167417,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T03:30:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26a1e9d3d555c4b4999321146b54d3a86ae64a8b","tid":167417,"uid":26332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T03:33:41.000Z","msg":"Send返d資料返地球要幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"770a9b980c32edf7724421c38fb26396e922b4d0","tid":167417,"uid":39876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T09:01:13.000Z","msg":"載到幾多人先"},{"pid":"dcfe00689d5d3d00a6b51fda87e7478721e7d649","tid":167417,"uid":42350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T10:04:29.000Z","m